---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-sand border-t border-ink/8">
  <div class="container-x py-20">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="h-10 w-10" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect width="64" height="64" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF"/>
            <path d="M 8 38 Q 18 24 32 32 T 56 28" stroke="#D9472B" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="14" cy="38" r="3" fill="#2F5D3A"/>
            <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="3" fill="#E2B23A"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="28" r="3.6" fill="#D9472B"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="font-display leading-tight">
            <p class="text-lg text-ink">Hawaii Mobile Food</p>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-stone">Foundation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          A Hawai‘i 501(c)(3) telling the stories of the people who run food trucks
          across the islands — long-form on the site, short-form on Na Leo TV.
          Contributions are tax-deductible to the fullest extent allowed by law.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-lava mb-4">Site</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#podcast" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">Podcast</a></li>
          <li><a href="#programs" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">Programs</a></li>
          <li><a href="#vendors" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">For vendors</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#support" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">For funders</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-lava mb-4">Reach us</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink/80">
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:hello@hawaiimobilefoodfoundation.org" class="text-ink/80 hover:text-ink no-underline">
              hello@hawaiimobilefoodfoundation.org
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-ink/80 leading-snug">
            PO Box 59<br/>
            Papaikou, HI 96781
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone">
          <a href="#support" class="text-stone hover:text-ink no-underline">Donate →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="rule my-12" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-4 text-stone text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.16em]">
      <p>© {year} Hawaii Mobile Food Foundation · 501(c)(3) Hawai‘i</p>
      <p>Made with aloha · Built with Astro on GitHub Pages</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
